646            billingAddress, shippingMethod, externalTaxRateForShippingMethod, custom, locale,
647            deleteDaysAfterLastModification, origin, shippingRateInput, itemShippingAddresses, discountCodes);
648    }
649
650    /**
651     * builds CartDraft without checking for non null required values
652     */
653    public CartDraft buildUnchecked() {
654        return new CartDraftImpl(currency, key, customerId, customerEmail, customerGroup, anonymousId, store, country,
655            inventoryMode, taxMode, taxRoundingMode, taxCalculationMode, lineItems, customLineItems, shippingAddress,
656            billingAddress, shippingMethod, externalTaxRateForShippingMethod, custom, locale,
657            deleteDaysAfterLastModification, origin, shippingRateInput, itemShippingAddresses, discountCodes);
658    }
659
660    public static CartDraftBuilder of() {
661        return new CartDraftBuilder();
662    }
663
664    public static CartDraftBuilder of(final CartDraft template) {
665        CartDraftBuilder builder = new CartDraftBuilder();
666        builder.currency = template.getCurrency();
667        builder.key = template.getKey();
668        builder.customerId = template.getCustomerId();
669        builder.customerEmail = template.getCustomerEmail();
670        builder.customerGroup = template.getCustomerGroup();
671        builder.anonymousId = template.getAnonymousId();
672        builder.store = template.getStore();
673        builder.country = template.getCountry();
674        builder.inventoryMode = template.getInventoryMode();
675        builder.taxMode = template.getTaxMode();
676        builder.taxRoundingMode = template.getTaxRoundingMode();
677        builder.taxCalculationMode = template.getTaxCalculationMode();
678        builder.lineItems = template.getLineItems();
679        builder.customLineItems = template.getCustomLineItems();
680        builder.shippingAddress = template.getShippingAddress();
681        builder.billingAddress = template.getBillingAddress();
682        builder.shippingMethod = template.getShippingMethod();
683        builder.externalTaxRateForShippingMethod = template.getExternalTaxRateForShippingMethod();
684        builder.custom = template.getCustom();
685        builder.locale = template.getLocale();
686        builder.deleteDaysAfterLastModification = template.getDeleteDaysAfterLastModification();
687        builder.origin = template.getOrigin();
688        builder.shippingRateInput = template.getShippingRateInput();
689        builder.itemShippingAddresses = template.getItemShippingAddresses();
690        builder.discountCodes = template.getDiscountCodes();
691        return builder;
692    }
